So today has been strange at best to say, First i will give you a brief recap. I moved here 1200 miles away from my family that lives in Michigan/Ohio area and have kept little to no contact with them for about 3 years so far. Today i get a letter from my grandparents that i havent even really spoke with for years prior to my move telling me about their Lexus, 2 spot camping lot w/ stretch golf cart to drive around and their 2 times a week bowling leagues..... That enough would have been enough family contact to last me threw the holidays but we arent nearly done yet. Phone rings its a area code and number i dont know so i answer it the lady on the other end says "Is Halie there?" i reply "This is" followed by that line we all love when the phone rings and we dont know who the hell it is, "Do you know who this is?"  my reply "Not a clue".... It was my Aunt Shirley from Michigan, This actually pleased me out of my entire family that includes over 25 cousins and even more aunts and uncles these are the only ones i actually think about more then once a year. Growing up i was raised with them pretty much they have 1 daughter a few years older then myself and 2 twin boys that are my age. All good family memories involve this section of the family. So i was happy to talk with her and find out how everyone was doing. My cousin Josh i had already known had been sent to Iraq at the start of the war so i had been worried about him alot. All is well with them good news, Until she gets another call and places me on hold. A few short minutes later she comes back and is like "What are the odds of this" and procedes to tell me that the call on the other line was from Ohio and my Uncle Scott was just life flighted to the hospital after a factory accident involving his clothes getting stuck and him drug threw a large machine. She lets me go so she can talk with them and get all the details. When she calls back she tells me what happend and that they think he will be ok but he has lost alot of skin and blood but lucky his clothes ripped off of it would have been alot worse. So we chat a bit longer and exchange contact info so we can keep in touch. After i hang up with her i figure i should call my father to make sure he knows about this seeing at it is his brother Scott that he is close to and actually works acrossed the street from. As i call y dad he was already on the way out the door because he was told at work, he says he actually saw the life flight helicopter land acrossed the street and knew some one was being transported but had no ideal it was his brother. Today has been crazy and all teh more reassures my theories that everyone in the Lambert family has ESP. Anytime there is any family contact its like this for me and people wonder why i dont answer my phone.... Now i think to cap off the day i will call my mother i mean hell its already a record amount of family members i spoke with today i should finish off the list with her. Wish me luck!

Wow, i am happy in a way but the happiness is sort of dulled out by the thoughts of days to come and the ignorant attitudes of people coming. Yes Bush won, Kerry actually admitted it, he gave his concession speech. Some how that just will not be enough for all the cry baby Kerry fans who will come up with all of your conspiracy theories. "All the votes have been stolen, this was rigged, it doesn't make a difference, the man always fucks us"... Blah Blah Blah. Get the fuck over it, deal with it. Kerry gave a nice little speech and carried himself with dignity, and threw in the towel  when he knew that he wasnt the better man for the job. Don't disgrace him now by running around crying just because you aren't happy with the outcome. Grow up, suck it up buck-o you guys lost.

Well  here she comes, already lost power for an hour or so here this  morning. Its about 1:45pm and i havent slept from the night before...... I'm sure i wont be able to sleep in a few hours when the hurricane is in full force either.... Well i guess this will most likely be good-bye for awhile cause all of civilation will be cut off shorty til who knows when.

All i can say about this entire hurricane bullshit is.... I DON'T WANT ANOTHER FUCKING ONE!!! Fuck Florida, Fuck Hurricanes, Fuck no electricity, Fuck dirty water, Fuck no gasoline, Fuck living on the 3rd (top) floor, Fuck trees that come out of the ground, Fuck 24 hours of 140 mile strong winds, Fuck having to put cold rags on your head just to sleep cause its so fucking hot, Fuck ice cold showers in the dark, Fuck peeing by candlelight, Fuck waking up to screaming ass children outside the windows that have to be open at 8am cause its already 90 degrees outside, Fuck no internet to rant and bitch on, Fuck everyone who lives outside of Florida that doesn't have to deal with this bullshit, Fuck mandatory evacuation and having to listen to ignorant ass spanish speaking people ramble, Fuck K-Mart not having and candles or batteries already, Fuck not being able to play video games, Fuck that mildew, moldy smell of all the food spoiling in the fridge, Fuck having to play cards all day, Fuck driving around on your last gallon of gas to try to find something thats open and coming home with no luck, Fuck sitting and waiting for the power to come back on magically, Fuck having to sleep without the sound of a fan, Fuck D-size batteries costing $6 for a 4 pack and the radio needing 6 to work, Fuck having to choose between buying food to eat or candles to see with, Fuck this cold/flu i have had for over a week, OK i am done for now, feel free to reply with your list of things to fuck that i may have forgotten. If i think of any more i will be sure to add them as the hour or doom come closer.

I really need to not be alone right now...
End.

Life as i know it ends soon......

Yes i do know that just about every post i leave on this is just me bitching on how i'm discontent with my life, Yet here starts another one... Everything seems so "watered down" so pointless anymore, days and weeks pass by so quickly without any real advancement in my life. I'm stuck at a point where i do not know what to do anymore. I think about the past and think maybe i made bad choices sometimes, other times i know i did everything as i should have. I have been thinking alot lately about just giving up and going "home" (Ohio), but i have less there then i do here really. Nothing is clear all the lines are blurry and feelings are smeared together. I cant tell happy from sad, i cant tell if i miss certain points in time of my life or if i am glad they are done and over with. Theres people that i would give anything in the world to have here with me right now, but when they are around all i want is to be alone. I cant do this any more i cant "live" like this... I cant count the amount of times i have cried myself to sleep and all the lost hours i have spent in this state of mind. I have always been depressed, maybe i just was'nt meant to be..... anything.
"Just think of me as your own personal trauma-sponge."

So today while i was in Wal-Mart i saw this old lady fall down an hurt herself, everyone was all panicking and running to get help. I could'nt help but to just smirk an chuckle to myself, as i did i turned my head and there was another woman just giving me some horrible stink-eye... It was WONDERFUL. I guess the normal public frowns upon you getting humor out of the pain and suffering of the elderly community, who would have known.
I'm wrong about a lot of things, too bad i was'nt wrong about you...

Today was wonderful, i slept in as late as i wanted to, i did nothing for hours, took a really long hot shower an got all girlie-fied for no reason, went out to dinner, stop an visitited a few places i havent gotten to in awhile. I like to piss people off, i like to make for akward situations, i like to keep people on their toes. Its amazing how much damage one can cause without any intent.

So you say i act like i don't care, So you say i show no emotion, Well how about his... FUCK YOU!!! Was that the emotion you wanted? Well maybe you should have tried to get it another way then... I will smile when you are a around and pretend you don't phase me, while your gone i will tell myself not to answer next time you call... xoxo <3 xoxo

So alot of this shitty things have been happening to me lately in my life, Broken car, no money, getting sick, things like that. Also people have really been letting me down alot, I do not have many people that i really call "Friends" but the ones i do i hold close to my heart and i try to be there for. This same respect does not seem to be given to me... Like i go out of my way to do things they ask and then they don't seem to care, i ask for a favor they have too much other shit to do that they don't even remember i asked. Fuck it!! I'm done now, this is as pointless as they are.. Goodbye my dearest.

Today was pretty good to be honest... i worked only for a few hours and made some good tips, i came home and i did my laundry and just sat around and was lazy for a few hours. After that i took a shower and threw myself together. I hung out with the ex-boy tonight it was pretty enjoyable, we just drove around for awhile trying to think of what to do then ended up at some wing place and ate some wings and chatted. We ended up going and jumpin the fence to the pool in the apartment complex we used to live in and went swimming and sat in the hot tub. It was nice seeing him and getting along with him, even tho we have so many reasons to be all pissy and bitchy to each other its still nice to put all that aside and just have fun every once in awhile. He has drama in his life he needs to deal with and get his shit together, my life is no better really so i cant tell him what to do. Anyways, it was a OK day all in all and now i will try to pass out because my sleeping medication is kickin in... Oh yea and there is a scary spider i keep seeing crawling around on my desk.. ICK!

Like a brick wall the memories smash into my fragile head.... They are bitter sweet at points... The air feels really thick right now like every breath i take is harder then the last... I think im breaking, it has been along time since this has happened, it is almost a comfortable feeling is a sadistic way. I remember the feeling and the sight of blood running over pale white skin, i remember laying in the fetal position crying until i passed out, i remember screaming until my throat swelled shut, i remember everything you ever said to me... i remember swallowing pills just to try to take the feeling of everything else away.. all of that sounds much better then the way i feel right now... i think a visit to the bathroom floor is well needed...

Well yesterday i woke up in the most pain i have ever felt in my life.. i was pukeing and really hot feeling an felt all dizzy... it was scary. So i called Mike and he came home from school and took me to the hospital, after being there for 7 hours and them pokeing me all all kinds of needles and giving me X-Rays, Cat scans & an a Pelvic exam they figure out i have kidney stones.... So needless to say this has not been a fun past 2 days, they gave me a bottle of Percocets tho so thats always a plus... i went to work today and came home after 4pm and thought that i should take a nap.. i just woke up 7 hours later from my "nap"... So now im going to have to try to sleep somehow again and get up to go to work in the morning.. this will be fun.. Well im going to get going for now i guess i kinda feel like crap ad im a bit sad...

Well i am pretty much over my cold now i think, my nose is still a bit runny but feeling better.. Now my tooth has started hurting me again the past couple days.. its VERY VERY bad it should have been pulled out years ago.. i cannot explain in words the way it hurts. New job is going pretty good im starting to catch on, i am done with training now so i will start taking tables alone and making tips finally.. We still have no money to pay rent, so soon my new home might be my car.... All and all even with all of this bad stuff going on im feeling ok and not totally depressed. I mean it comes and goes but im doing ok i guess... I miss a few people and im always around a few others that i could live with out seeing daily.. but what else can i say...

I'm sleeping alone, and at that my brain is catapulted into the present time... it is a really unnerving feeling to lay there in the dark for a few minutes after-wards listening to my spastic heart beat...
